=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template\"><code>&lt;template&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/HTML/Element/video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>The <strong>HTML Disclosure Summary element</strong> (<strong><code>&lt;summary&gt;</code></strong>) element specifies a summary, caption, or legend for a <a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/HTML/Element/details\"><code>&lt;details&gt;</code></a> element's disclosure box. Clicking the <code>&lt;summary&gt;</code> element toggles the state of the parent <code>&lt;details&gt;</code> element open and closed.</p><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"375\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/tabbed/summary.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Permitted content</th>\n      <th><a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\">Phrasing content</a> or one element of <a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#heading_content\">Heading content</a></th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Tag omission</td>\n      <td>None, both the start tag and the end tag are mandatory.</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Permitted parents</td>\n      <td>The <a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/HTML/Element/details\"><code>&lt;details&gt;</code></a> element.</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Permitted ARIA roles</td>\n      <td><code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#button\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">button</a></code></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>DOM interface</td>\n      <td><a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"атрибуты","title":"Атрибуты","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Этот элемент включает только <a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes\">глобальные атрибуты</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"примечания","title":"Примечания","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Содержимым элемента <code>&lt;summary&gt;</code> может быть любой заголовок, простой текст или HTML, которые можно использовать в абзаце.</p>\n<p>Элемент <code>&lt;summary&gt;</code> может быть использован в качестве потомка элемента <code>&lt;details&gt;</code> . Когда пользователь кликает по элементу summary, его родитель - <code>&lt;details&gt;</code> меняет состояние с раскрытого или закрытого на обратное,и тогда <code><a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/Reference/Events/toggle\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">toggle</a></code> event is sent to the <code>&lt;details&gt;</code> element, which can be used to let you know when this state change occurs.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"default_label_text","title":"Default label text","isH3":true,"content":"<p>If a <code>&lt;details&gt;</code> element's first child is not a <code>&lt;summary&gt;</code> element, the <a href=\"/ru/docs/Glossary/User_agent\">user agent</a> will use a default string (typically \"Details\") as the label for the disclosure box.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"default_style","title":"Default style","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Per the HTML specification, the default style for <code>&lt;summary&gt;</code> elements includes <code>display: list-item</code>. This makes it possible to change or remove the icon displayed as the disclosure widget next to the label from the default, which is typically a triangle.</p>\n<p>You can also change the style to <code>display: block</code> to remove the disclosure triangle.</p>\n<p>See the <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">Browser compatibility</a> section for details, as not all browsers support full functionality of this element yet.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"примеры","title":"Примеры","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Below are some examples showing <code>&lt;summary&gt;</code> in use. You can find more examples in the documentation for the <a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/HTML/Element/details\"><code>&lt;details&gt;</code></a> element.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"простой_пример","title":"Простой пример","isH3":true,"content":"<p>A simple example showing the use of <code>&lt;summary&gt;</code> in a <a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/HTML/Element/details\"><code>&lt;details&gt;</code></a> element:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>details</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">open</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>summary</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Overview<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>summary</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ol</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Cash on hand: $500.00<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Current invoice: $75.30<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Due date: 5/6/19<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ol</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>details</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Простой пример sample\" id=\"frame_простой_пример\" width=\"650\" height=\"120\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/ru/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary/_sample_.%D0%BF%D1%80%D0%BE%D1%81%D1%82%D0%BE%D0%B9_%D0%BF%D1%80%D0%B8%D0%BC%D0%B5%D1%80.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summaries_as_headings","title":"Summaries as headings","isH3":true,"content":"<p>You can use heading elements in <code>&lt;summary&gt;</code>, like this:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>details</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">open</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>summary</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Overview<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>summary</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ol</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Cash on hand: $500.00<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Current invoice: $75.30<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Due date: 5/6/19<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ol</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>details</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Summaries as headings sample\" id=\"frame_summaries_as_headings\" width=\"650\" height=\"120\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/ru/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary/_sample_.summaries_as_headings.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>\n<p>This currently has some spacing issues that could be addressed using CSS.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html_in_summaries","title":"HTML in summaries","isH3":true,"content":"<p>This example adds some semantics to the <code>&lt;summary&gt;</code> element to indicate the label as important:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>details</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">open</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>summary</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>strong</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Overview<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>strong</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>summary</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ol</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Cash on hand: $500.00<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Current invoice: $75.30<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Due date: 5/6/19<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ol</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>details</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"HTML in summaries sample\" id=\"frame_html_in_summaries\" width=\"650\" height=\"120\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/ru/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary/_sample_.html_in_summaries.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Specifications","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Specification</th>\n      <th>Status</th>\n      <th>Comment</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/interactive-elements.html#the-summary-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"ru\">Определение '&lt;summary&gt;' в этой спецификации.</small></a></td>\n      <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Живой стандарт</span></td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html51/interactive-elements.html#the-summary-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 5.1<br><small lang=\"ru\">Определение '&lt;summary&gt;' в этой спецификации.</small></a></td>\n      <td><span class=